        },
        {
          "tag": "a",
          "text": "Get Ready to Apply Are you ready to start your application?  Let us walk you through the admissions process to apply to be an undergraduate, first-year student. We\u2019re so excited that you\u2019re interested",
          "ariaLabel": "",
          "classes": "group inline-block border relative rounded p-8 overflow-hidden o-10 col-span-4 grid-item bg-blue-700 border-blue-700 text-white pb-16",
