          "w": 387,
          "h": 352
        },
        {
          "tag": "a",
          "text": "Explore Different Majors Choosing a major is an important decision and we've got you covered in helping to choose with our new tool the Degree Finder. Explore all of our majors and get started on your",
          "ariaLabel": "",
          "classes": "group inline-block border relative rounded p-8 overflow-hidden o-10 col-span-4 grid-item bg-blue-300 border-blue-300 text-black pb-16 transition duration-200 transform hover:rotate-1",
